== Access == * 5-minute walk from {{ill|Gamo Yonchome Station|ja|蒲生四丁目駅|qq=draft}} on the {{ill|Osaka Metro Nagahori Tsurumi-ryokuchi Line|ja|Osaka Metro長堀鶴見緑地線|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Osaka Metro Imazato Line|ja|Osaka Metro今里筋線|qq=draft}} * Approximately 10 minutes by car from {{ill|Morinomiya Exit|ja|森之宮出入口|qq=draft}} on the {{ill|Hanshin Expressway Route 17 Nishi-Osaka Line|ja|阪神高速17号西大阪線|qq=draft}}
